name: Melancholy of the Porcelain doll
description:
Lying under the reflections of colourful stained glass, there lies a porcelain doll
Brought unwillingly into the world of humans , only to be left under the shelf...
Facing the dark wall, peeking through the window the Winter moonlight shines upon her coldly
Wishing to have lived a lovely life inside her lifeless body, looking outside the window through her lively eyes watching the buildings surrounded by ice
The merciless gods above the sky never heard her cries.
